      tee.  For this meeting, Corfield, Hartinger, and Unruh will also par-
      ticipate.  Also, each ad hoc working group (WG) chair is responsible to
      bring that WG's motions to, and participate in, the drafting committee.
      Lenkov added that each chair may delegate the job to another WG member,
